result.name: pendle-government-procurement-card-spend
result.notes:
The government recommends that local authorities publish all expenditure made on government procurement cards (GPC). (Please note, areas may be redacted as they may be commercially sensitive or there may be data protection issues). 

The following details are not included because other purchasing tools and processes are used as the Councils main function for making payments of this kind:
i) Supplier registered charity number 
ii) VCSE grant
